e arranged to be viewers aged 15 or older.</ref> Starting from the ninth episode, for the realness of the drama to be shown, the rating will be altered back to 19.<ref>{{cite web|first=Hyang-hee|last=Jin|url=https://entertain.naver.com/now/read?oid=009&aid=0004562502|title=\u2018\ubd80\ubd80\uc758 \uc138\uacc4\u2019 9\ud68c~16\ud68c 19\u7981 \uacb0\uc815 \u201c\ud604\uc2e4\uac10 \uc704\ud574\u201d|date=April 23, 2020|accessdate=April 23, 2020|website=Maeil Kyungje|publisher=Naver|language=ko}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{Official website|http://tv.jtbc.joins.com/theworldofthemarried}} {{in lang|ko}}\n* {{Hancinema drama|The_Married_Life}}\n* {{IMDb title|tt12042964}}\n\n{{Kang Eun-kyung}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:World of the Married, The}}\n[[Category:Joongang Tongyang Broadcasting Company television dramas]]\n[[Category:Korean-language television programs]]\n[[Category:2020s South Korean television series]]\n[[Category:2020 South Korean television series debuts]]\n<!-- [[Category:2020 South Korean television series endings]] -->\n[[Category:South Korean drama television series]]\n[[Category:Adultery in television]]\n[[Category:South Korean television series based on British television series]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|2020 South Korean television series}}\n{{Infobox television\n| show_name                = The World of the Married\n| show_name_2              = A World of Married Couple<ref>{{cite video|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MtiPX82dkus|title=A World of Married Couple Trailer #2|publisher=Viu Singapore|website=YouTube|date=March 2, 2020}}</ref>\n| image                    = The_World_of_the_Married.jpg\n| caption                  = Promotional poster\n| native_name              = {{Infobox name module|hangul=\ubd80\ubd80\uc758 \uc138\uacc4|hanja=\u592b\u5a66\uc758 \u4e16\u754c}}\n| genre                    = [[Drama (film and television)|Drama]]\n| creator                  = [[Kang Eun-kyung]]\n| based_on       